                 By <a href="/geforce/author/andrew-burnes/" class="author-link" target="_blank">Andrew Burnes</a> on May 19, 2026 | <span class="article-comp-tags"> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">Featured Stories</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">Frame Generation</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">GeForce RTX 50 Series</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">GeForce RTX GPUs</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">Multi Frame Generation</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">NVIDIA App</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">NVIDIA DLSS</a></span> </span>
                </div>
               </div>
              </div>
