                    <div class="text-left lap-text-left tab-text-left mob-text-left">
                     <div class="description ">
                      <p>At 1920x1080 on GeForce RTX 50 Series Laptops, a 3.9X DLSS performance multiplier sees <em>Forza Horizon 6</em>’s max setting, ray-traced frame rates hit 330 FPS, for super fast on-the-go gaming on GeForce RTX 5090, 5080 and 5070 Ti Laptop GPUs.</p>
